column2:
1.竞技场中战斗需要消耗<color=#ffcd00>竞技次数</color>，每次消耗1点，竞技次数每小时恢复1点
2.玩家必须设置自己的<color=#ffcd00>防御阵容</color>，抵御其他玩家的挑战，防守失败也会扣分的哦
3.若对匹配的对手不满意，可以通过<color=#ffcd00>花费金币刷新对手</color>
4.竞技场中战斗采取<color=#ffcd00>5V5</color>的方式，战斗过程是<color=#ffcd00>全自动</color>的，不能手动操作。
5.竞技成功时，会获得<color=#ffcd00>荣誉点</color>奖励，荣誉点可以用来在<color=#ffcd00>竞技商店</color>中换取物品
6.若与敌人僵持不下，出现平局按钮后，可以选择以<color=#ffcd00>平局</color>结束本场竞技，平局仍会得到1点荣誉点
7.根据每场战斗的结果（包括平局）以及竞技双方的积分，玩家增减的<color=#ffcd00>竞技积分</color>也会不同
8.<color=#ffcd00>竞技积分</color>是评价玩家段位的唯一标准，当然，也是排行榜排名的唯一标准
9.竞技场每周周一凌晨1点都会根据玩家当时所在段位发放一次<color=#ffcd00>段位奖励</color>，奖励通过邮件发放
10.竞技场中，每个赛季持续四周，赛季结束时，排名前100的玩家会获得<color=#ffcd00>排名奖励</color>，奖励通过邮件发放，记得查收哦
11.竞技场<color=#ffcd00>前100名</color>的排行数据每10分钟刷新一次

黄金三阶                1600~1699

白银二阶                1400~1499
白银三阶                1300~1399

青铜三阶                1099及以下
column3:
1. Each battle in the Arena requires <color=#ffcd00>1 Arena</color> entry. Your Arena entries recover at a rate of 1 per hour.
2. Players must set their own <color=#ffcd00>defense</color> to defend against other players' challenges. Points are deducted when a player's defense is defeated.
3. The opponent you are matched against can be <color=#ffcd00>changed by spending Coins</color>.
4. The Arena uses a <color=#ffcd00>5v5</color> battle setting. The battles will be fought using <color=#ffcd00>auto-battle</color>, and abilities cannot be manually cast.
5. When players are victorious in the Arena, they will receive <color=#ffcd00>Honor Points</color>. These points can be used to purchase items in the <color=#ffcd00>Arena Store</color>.
6. If the battle turns into a stalemate between you and the opponent, a Draw button will appear, and the battle can be ended as a <color=#ffcd00>draw</color>. A draw will still award 1 Honor Point.
7. The amount of <color=#ffcd00>Arena Points</color> added or deducted will be calculated according to the battle results(including draws) and the Arena Point amounts of both players.
8. <color=#ffcd00>Arena Points</color> are the standard for determining a player's Arena Title, as well as their Arena Ranking.
9. <color=#ffcd00>Rewards based upon players' current Arena Titles</color> will be sent via in-game mail each week on Monday at 1:00am.
10. Each Arena season lasts for 4 weeks. After a season finishes, players ranking in the top 100 will receive a <color=#ffcd00>ranking reward</color> via in-game mail. So remember to keep an eye out for that!
11. The <color=#ffcd00>top 100</color> player rankings are updated every 10 minutes.

Arena Points and Titles
Title                       Arena Pts.
Master Rank 1       2100 and above
Master Rank 2       2000~2099
Master Rank 3       1900~1999
Gold Rank 1           1800~1899
Gold Rank 2           1700~1799
Gold Rank 3           1600~1699
Silver Rank 1          1500~1599
Silver Rank 2          1400~1499
Silver Rank 3          1300~1399
Bronze Rank 1        1200~1299
Bronze Rank 2        1100~1199
Bronze Rank 3        1099 and below
column4:
1.競技場中戰鬥需要消耗<color=#ffcd00>競技次數</color>，每次消耗1點，競技次數每小時恢復1點
2.玩家必須設定自己的<color=#ffcd00>防禦陣容</color>，抵禦其他玩家的挑戰，防守失敗也會扣分的哦
3.若對匹配的對手不滿意，可以通過<color=#ffcd00>花費金幣刷新對手</color>
4.競技場中戰鬥採取<color=#ffcd00>5V5</color>的方式，戰鬥過程是<color=#ffcd00>全自動</color>的，不能手動操作。
5.競技成功時，會獲得<color=#ffcd00>榮譽點</color>獎勵，榮譽點可以用來在<color=#ffcd00>競技商店</color>中換取物品
6.若與敵人僵持不下，出現平局按鈕後，可以選擇以<color=#ffcd00>平局</color>結束本場競技，平局仍會得到1點榮譽點
7.<color=#ffcd00>競技積分</color>是評價玩家階級的唯一標準，當然，也是排行榜排名的唯一標準
9.競技場每週週一淩晨1點都會根據玩家當時所在階級發放一次<color=#ffcd00>階級獎勵</color>，獎勵通過信件發放
10.競技場中，每個賽季持續四周，賽季結束時，排名前100的玩家會獲得<color=#ffcd00>排名獎勵</color>，獎勵通過信件發放，記得查收哦
11.競技場<color=#ffcd00>前100名</color>的排行資料每10分鐘刷新一次

column4: 使用信仰之力是提升寵物等級的最快方法。

column2: 宠物装备可以打造，打造能够大幅提升装备战力。
column3: Monster equipment can be forged. Forging equipment greatly increases the equipment's effectiveness in battle.
column4: 寵物裝備可以打造，打造能夠大幅提升裝備戰力。

column2: 宠物有白、绿、蓝、紫、橙、红六个品质，通过进阶能够达到更高品质。
column3: Monsters have White, Green, Blue, Purple, Orange, and Red grades. Monster grades can be increased via Advance.
column4: 寵物有白、綠、藍、紫、橙、紅六個品質，通過進階能夠達到更高品質。

column2: 宠物装备有白、绿、蓝、紫、橙、红六个品质，通过打造能够达到更高品质。
column3: Monster equipment has White, Green, Blue, Purple, Orange, and Red grades. Monster equipment grades can be increased via Forging.
column4: 寵物裝備有白、綠、藍、紫、橙、紅六個品質，通過打造能夠達到更高品質。

column2: 蓝色及以上品质的装备可以镶嵌纹章。
column3: Insignia can be attached into equipment Blue grade and above.
column4: 藍色及以上品質的裝備可以鑲嵌紋章。

column2: 9种纹章提升的属性不同，选择适合宠物的才是明智之举。
column3: 9 different kinds of Insignia affect equipment atrributes differently, so make sure to choose the Insignia that best suits your monster.
column4: 9種紋章提升的屬性不同，選擇適合寵物的才是明智之舉。

column2: 纹章有白、绿、蓝、紫、橙、红六个品质，通过合成能够达到更高品质。
column3: Insignia have White, Green, Blue, Purple, Orange, and Red grades. Insignia grades can be increased via Combining.
column4: 紋章有白、綠、藍、紫、橙、紅六個品質，通過合成能夠達到更高品質。

column2: 商店根据顾客的等级，商品的品质也会有所不同。
column3: Items in the store may vary according to the level of the customer!
column4: 商店根據顧客的等級，商品的品質也會有所不同。

column2: 商店每天固定时间刷新商品，常去逛逛~
column3: The Store will be refreshed with new items at set times each day. Make sure to check for new items often!
column4: 商店每天固定時間刷新商品，常去逛逛~

column2: 分解掉没有用处的装备，变废为宝。
column3: Remember to discard any unneeded equipment.
column4: 分解掉沒有用處的裝備，變廢為寶。

column2: 纹章和有些材料能够通过合成获得更高品质的。
column3: Insignias and some materials can be improved to a higher grade via Combining.
column4: 紋章和有些材料能夠通過合成獲得更高品質的。

column2: 还在独自战斗？快加入公会，寻找一起并肩作战的小伙伴吧~
column3: Still battling alone? Join a Guild and fight side by side with some new friends!
column4: 還在獨自戰鬥？快加入公會，尋找一起並肩作戰的小夥伴吧~

column2: 参与公会活动，获得的贡献值能够在公会商店中兑换各种道具。
column3: Participate in Guild events to receive Contribution Points that can be used in the Guild Store to purchase equipment.
column4: 參與公會活動，獲得的貢獻值能夠在公會商店中兌換各種道具。

column2: 将一些空闲的宠物派去大冒险，会有意想不到的收获哦~
column3: Send some of your free monsters to go on adventures. They might discover something you didn't expect!
column4: 將一些空閒的寵物派去大冒險，會有意想不到的收穫哦~

column2: 要尝试满足大冒险的额外奖励获得条件，才能获得丰厚的奖励。
column3: Try to complete the bonus reward requirements in Adventures to receive some awesome bonus rewards!
column4: 要嘗試滿足大冒險的額外獎勵獲得條件，才能獲得豐厚的獎勵。

column2: 每个章节获得6个星星、12个星星、24个星星时，都可以领取对应的宝箱奖励哦！
column3: Rewards may be collected upon receiving 6 stars, 12 stars, and 24 stars for each chapter.
column4: 每個章節獲得6個星星、12個星星、24個星星時，都可以領取對應的寶箱獎勵哦！

column2: “扫荡”操作是节省时间的最佳方式！
column3: Using "Raid Passes" is the best way to save time!
column4: “掃蕩”操作是節省時間的最佳方式！

column2: 三星通关副本后可以获得该副本的“扫荡”使用权。
column3: Clearing a stage with a 3-Star rating will grant you the ability to use Raid Passes.
column4: 三星通關副本後可以獲得該副本的“掃蕩”使用權。

column2: 合理搭配阵容，配合使用照妖镜可以确保你安全通关。
column3: A smart line-up in combination with using the Mytho Lens can do a lot to ensure your victory.
column4: 合理搭配陣容，配合使用照妖鏡可以確保你安全通關。

column2: 战斗前长按头像查看敌方信息，合理布置宠物。
column3: Before the battle, you can tap and hold on enemy avatars to view more information needed to adjust your line-up.
column4: 戰鬥前長按頭像查看敵方資訊，合理佈置寵物。

column2: BOSS的弱点有的有血条，能够被打掉；有的没有血条，不能被打掉。
column3: Some Boss weakpoints have a certain amount of HP and can be destroyed. Others have no HP, and cannot.
column4: BOSS的弱點有的有血條，能夠被打掉；有的沒有血條，不能被打掉。

column2: 战斗中适当换怪，可以带来避免怪物死亡、积攒大招等等好处哦~
column3: Get used to swapping monsters in battle. It will help you avoid losing monsters in battle and allow you to combine their ultimate abilities.
column4: 戰鬥中適當換怪，可以帶來避免怪物死亡、積攢大招等等好處哦~

column2: 打掉弱点多数情况是好的，但是也有例外哟！
column3: Destroying weakpoints is good in most cases, but remember that there are exceptions!
column4: 打掉弱點多數情況是好的，但是也有例外喲！

column2: 集火操作能够集中我方火力，快速攻下敌方小怪或者弱点目标。
column3: Concentrating fire from your monsters' attacks can help you quickly defeat enemy monsters, and deal more damage to enemy weakpoints.
column4: 集火操作能夠集中我方火力，快速攻下敵方小怪或者弱點目標。

column2: 米达斯宫能够产出大量金币，快来挑战吧！
column3: You can earn large amounts of Coins in Palace of Midas, give it a try!
column4: 米達斯宮能夠產出大量金幣，快來挑戰吧！

column2: 在米达斯宫，难度越高获得的金币也就越多，加油挑战吧！
column3: The higher the diffculties, the more Coins can be earned in Palace of Midas. Fighting!
column4: 在米達斯宮，難度越高獲得的金幣也就越多，加油挑戰吧！

column2: 每周日米达斯宫和至福乐土都会开放，快来挑战吧！
column3: Palace of Midas and Fields of Elysium will both open every Sunday. Make sure to give it a try!
column4: 每週日米達斯宮和至福樂土都會開放，快來挑戰吧！

column2: 至福乐土能够产出大量信仰之力，快来挑战吧！
column3: You can earn large amounts of Mytho Essences in Fields of Elysium, give it a try!
column4: 至福樂土能夠產出大量信仰之力，快來挑戰吧！

column2: 在至福乐土，难度越高获得的信仰之力也就越多，加油挑战吧！
column3: The higher the difficulty, the more Mytho Essence that can be earned in Fields of Elysium. Fighting!
column4: 在至福樂土，難度越高獲得的信仰之力也就越多，加油挑戰吧！

column2: 通天塔每月1号都会刷新进度，刷新后可重新进行挑战。
column3: Tower Of Darkness progress will be refreshed on the first day of each month.
column4: 通天塔每月1號都會刷新進度，刷新後可重新進行挑戰。

column2: 通天塔每过5层就会给一个阶段性奖励，快来挑战吧！
column3: The Tower Of Darkness will grant you a reward every 5 levels, give it a try!
column4: 通天塔每過5層就會給一個階段性獎勵，快來挑戰吧！

column2: 通天塔掉落的暗黑碎片可以在通天塔商店兑换奖励。
column3: The Dark Fragment that drops from the Tower of Darkness can be used to exchange in the Tower Store.
column4: 通天塔掉落的暗黑碎片可以在通天塔商店兌換獎勵。

column2: 挑战每座塔的层数越高，难度也就越大，同时阶段奖励也会越好。
column3: Difficulty will increase with every level of the Tower Of Darkness, and the 5-level reward will also increase in value.
column4: 挑戰每座塔的層數越高，難度也就越大，同時階段獎勵也會越好。

column2: 清楚的了解boss的技能和弱点，能够帮助你更好的战胜它。
column3: Make sure you understand Boss weakpoints and abilities to help you defeat it more easily.
column4: 清楚的瞭解boss的技能和弱點，能夠幫助你更好的戰勝它。

column2: 运用克制boss的宠物，能够帮助你更好的战胜它。
column3: Try to use monsters that are strong against each boss to make the battle go in your favor.
column4: 運用克制boss的寵物，能夠幫助你更好的戰勝它。

column2: 合理的运用照妖镜，集火与换怪，能够让你通关到更高层。
column3: Use the Mytho Lens and concentrate your monsters' fire to help you complete higher stages.
column4: 合理的運用照妖鏡，集火與換怪，能夠讓你通關到更高層。

column2: 竞技场中战斗需要消耗竞技点数，每次消耗1点。竞技点数每小时恢复1点。
column3: Each battle in the Arena requires 1 Arena entry. Your Arena entries recover at a rate of 1 per hour.
column4: 競技場中戰鬥需要消耗競技點數，每次消耗1點。競技點數每小時恢復1點。

column2: 玩家必须设置自己的防御阵容，抵御其他玩家的挑战，防守失败也会扣分的哦~
column3: Players must set their own defense to defend against other players' challenges. Points are deducted when a player's defense is defeated.
column4: 玩家必須設定自己的防禦陣容，抵禦其他玩家的挑戰，防守失敗也會扣分的哦~

column2: 若对匹配的对手不满意，可以通过花费金币刷新对手。
column3: The opponent you are matched against can be changed by spending Coins.
column4: 若對匹配的對手不滿意，可以通過花費金幣刷新對手。

column2: 竞技场中战斗采取5V5的方式。
column3: The Arena uses a 5v5 battle setting.
column4: 競技場中戰鬥採取5V5的方式。

column2: 竞技场的战斗过程是全自动的，不能手动操作。
column3: Arena battles are fought using auto-battle, and abilities cannot be manually cast.
column4: 競技場的戰鬥過程是全自動的，不能手動操作。

column2: 竞技成功时，会获得荣誉点奖励，荣誉点可以用来在竞技商店中换取物品。
column3: When players are victorious in the Arena, they will receive Honor Points. These points can be used to purchase items in the Arena Store.
column4: 競技成功時，會獲得榮譽點獎勵，榮譽點可以用來在競技商店中換取物品。

column2: 根据每场战斗的结果以及竞技双方的积分，玩家增减的竞技积分也会不同。
column3: The amount of Arena Points added or deducted will be calculated according to the battle results and the Arena Point amounts of both players.
column4: 根據每場戰鬥的結果以及競技雙方的積分，玩家增減的競技積分也會不同。

column2:
1.玩家每天均可以挑战<color=#ffcd00>9个</color>神话的守护者。
2.9个神话守护者的难度会根据玩家当日挑战成功的<color=#ffcd00>次数</color>逐渐<color=#ffcd00>提升</color>。
3.神话守护者们的实力会随着<color=#ffcd00>玩家能力提升而增强</color>。
4.已经阵亡的宠物<color=#ffcd00>无法继续上阵</color>，同时无法继续参加<color=#ffcd00>当日后续关卡</color>的挑战。
5.每一关结束后敌我双方的<color=#ffcd00>血量值</color>和<color=#ffcd00>能量值</color>均会继承到下次神话守护者的战斗中。
6.每次挑战成功均会获得<color=#ffcd00>大量奖励</color>，并有几率获得额外<color=#ffcd00>惊喜之书</color>奖励！
7.成功挑战最后一个神话守护者<color=#ffcd00>必定</color>会获得<color=#ffcd00>惊喜之书</color>奖励哦！
8.每个关卡只能<color=#ffcd00>成功挑战1次</color>，挑战失败后可以继续进行挑战，但是挑战失败不会获得任何奖励。
9.挑战成功后还可以获得<color=#ffcd00>书魂</color>，可以用于兑换<color=#ffcd00>丰富奖励</color>！

column2:
1.神怪入侵活动每天开放3场，玩家每天只能参与其中的1场。
    开放时间：每天中午12:45——13:00
                         每天晚上20:00——20:15
                         每天晚上21:45——22:00
2.每场神怪入侵活动中，可以通过提升士气来提升出战怪物的属性，出战宠物能够得到力量、智力、体力的全面提升！
   提升士气消耗钻石，在单场活动里，士气最高能被提升到100%。  
3.每个boss都有克星，当日只要将克星配置进阵容，全员获得指定buff加成。Buff能够叠加存在哦！
   低级克星buff：出战全员增加伤害10%
   高级克星buff：出战全员增加伤害20%
4.神怪入侵活动会根据个人对boss的总伤害量进行排名，伤害量越高，排名越靠前，奖励也就越丰厚哦！
5.每场活动持续时间为15分钟，本场活动的boss死亡或者活动时间到达后，本场活动结束。
6.如果单场活动boss被消灭，排名前100的玩家将根据排名获得不同的额外钻石奖励！排名越靠前，钻石越多哦！
    第1名               250钻石
    第2名               200钻石
    第3名               150钻石
    第4-20名          100钻石
    第21-100名      50钻石
column3:
1.Deity Invasion opens for 3 battles daily. Players may only participate in 1 of the 3 battles each day.
   Open every afternoon from 12:45 to 13:00
   Open every night from 20:00 to 20:15
   Open every night from 21:45 to 22:00
2.In each Deity Invasion battle, players can increase morale to increase their monsters' stats. Monsters can receive increases to STR, INT, and Power.
  Increasing moral requires diamonds. In one battle, morale can be upgraded up to 100%.
3.Each boss has a nemesis. Players simply need to put the nemesis in their lineup and all their monsters will receive the specified buff. This buff can be stacked!
  Minor nemesis buff: increases all monsters' damage by 10%
  Major nemesis buff: increases all monsters' damage by 20%
4.Monster Invasion will have rankings for each player based on total damage dealt to the boss. The higher the damage, the higher the ranking and the better the rewards!
5.Each Monster Invasion battle will last for 15 mintues. The battle will end when the boss dies or the time limit is reached.
6.If the boss is defeated, players ranked in the top 100 will receive bonus rewards based on their rankings. The higher the player ranking, the more diamonds that will be rewarded!
   Rank 1                     250 Diamonds
   Rank 2                     200 Diamonds
   Rank 3                     150 Diamonds
   Ranks 4 - 20            100 Diamonds
   Ranks 21 - 100        50   Diamonds

<color=#ffcc00>受星象运行影响,两界封印松动,灵界深处的罕见神怪苏醒侵扰人间,so……勇敢的少年快去收服神怪加固封印吧！</color>

1.“封印日”为<color=#ffcc00>每周六中午12点至周日中午12点</color>，开放期间玩家可以<color=#ffcc00>消耗活力</color>进行挑战。

2.每逢“封印日”封印松动之时，会由异界来临一位<color=#ffcc00>主战神怪</color>与一位<color=#ffcc00>辅战神怪</color>降临，玩家挑战成功则有机会获得该<color=#ffcc00>神怪的碎片</color>！

3.每次挑战需要经过<color=#ffcc00>9层</color>考验，通关层数<color=#ffcc00>越多</color>，获得主战神怪的碎片几率<color=#ffcc00>越大</color>、数量<color=#ffcc00>越多</color>！

4.“封印日”降临的神怪每周<color=#ffcc00>各不相同</color>，遇到喜欢的神怪要抓紧时间进行挑战哦！
column3:
<color=#ffcc00>As the constellations moved in the night sky, a rift has mysteriously appeared in the seal between the two worlds. Rare monsters from the depths of the spirit world have now been awakened and are moving to invade the real world. Warriors, we must move quickly to defend our world!</color>

1. “Rift Day” is open each Saturday<color=#ffcc00> from 12:00 noon to Sunday 12:00</color>. During the event time, players may <color=#ffcc00>spend Energy</color> to join the battles.

2. During the "Rift Day” event, players will be able to battle a <color=#ffcc00>deity monster</color> from Mythos along with its <color=#ffcc00>supporting monsters</color>. If the battle is successful, players have a chance of receiving that <color=#ffcc00>deity monster’s fragments</color>!

3. Each battle will require passing through <color=#ffcc00>9 trials</color>. With <color=#ffcc00>more trials</color> completed, players have <color=#ffcc00>better chances</color> of getting deity fragments, and receiving them in a <color=#ffcc00>larger amounts</color>!

4. The monsters that appear in “Rift Day” will be <color=#ffcc00>different each week</color>. If you encounter a deity monster that you want to collect, then take advantage of the opportunity and join the battle!
column4:
<color=#ffcc00>受星象運行影響,兩界封印松動,靈界深處的罕見神怪蘇醒侵擾人間,so……勇敢的少年快去收服神怪加固封印吧！</color>

1.“封印日”為<color=#ffcc00>每周六中午12點至周日中午12點</color>，開放期間玩家可以<color=#ffcc00>消耗活力</color>進行挑戰。

2.每逢“封印日”封印松動之時，會由異界來臨壹位<color=#ffcc00>主戰神怪</color>與壹位<color=#ffcc00>輔戰神怪</color>降臨，玩家挑戰成功則有機會獲得該<color=#ffcc00>神怪的碎片</color>！

3.每次挑戰需要經過<color=#ffcc00>9層</color>考驗，通關層數<color=#ffcc00>越多</color>，獲得主戰神怪的碎片幾率<color=#ffcc00>越大</color>、數量<color=#ffcc00>越多</color>！

4.“封印日”降臨的神怪每周<color=#ffcc00>各不相同</color>，遇到喜歡的神怪要抓緊時間進行挑戰哦！
